inoremap <C-K> <Up>
inoremap <C-J> <Down>
inoremap <C-H> <Left>
inoremap <C-L> <Right>
inoremap <C-U> <ESC>mzgUiw`za
inoremap <C-K> <ESC>mzguiw`za
